this integral?

00:00:18.290 --> 00:00:22.030
Well, the first integral I'm
integrating with respect to x.

00:00:22.030 --> 00:00:22.280
Right?

00:00:22.280 --> 00:00:24.770
I'm adding up the
little x sums.

00:00:24.770 --> 00:00:27.670
So I'm forming this
