Yeah, this is a 2.

00:02:48.270 --> 00:02:49.150
I don't know how I ended up.

00:02:49.150 --> 00:02:49.510
Right?

00:02:49.510 --> 00:02:52.270
Square root of y squared
is y, times y squared

00:02:52.270 --> 00:02:53.575
y to the third over 2.

00:02:57.470 --> 00:02:58.030
Right.

00:02:58.030 --> 00:03:00.900
And then when I take
the integral of this

00:03:00.900 --> 00:03:03.590
it's 4 times 2.

00:03:03.590 --> 00:03:04.240
8.

00:03:04.240 --> 00:03:06.670
Got to make sure I don't make
those careless mistakes.

