00:07:39.650 --> 00:07:41.950
So we go from x is equal to 0.

00:07:41.950 --> 00:07:45.060
And then our upper bound
is x is equal to 1.

00:07:45.060 --> 00:07:47.520
So x is equal to 0,
x is equal to 1.

00:07:47.520 --> 00:07:51.630
And in general, one way to
think about it is when you're

00:07:51.630 --> 00:07:56.020
doing kind of the last sum or
the last integral, you really

00:07:56.020 --> 00:07:59.160
