Because our final answer has
to be a number, assuming

00:08:03.120 --> 00:08:06.360
that we're not dealing with
something very, very abstract.

00:08:06.360 --> 00:08:07.980
But our final answer is
going to have a number.

00:08:07.980 --> 00:08:09.760
So if you had some variables
here you probably

00:08:09.760 --> 00:08:10.740
did something wrong.

00:08:10.740 --> 00:08:13.640
And it's always useful, I
think, to draw that little da

00:08:13.640 --> 00:08:16.160
and then figure out-- OK,
