00:08:20.210 --> 00:08:22.380
Oh, it's x squared. y
is equal to x squared.

00:08:22.380 --> 00:08:26.260
If I go down I bump into the
x-axis, or y is equal to 0.

00:08:26.260 --> 00:08:27.410
And so forth and so on.

00:08:27.410 --> 00:08:29.910
So now let's just evaluate
this and confirm that

00:08:29.910 --> 00:08:32.110
