00:08:58.800 --> 00:09:04.300
So we have x times x squared
to the third power, over 3.

00:09:04.300 --> 00:09:08.540
That equals x to the seventh.

00:09:08.540 --> 00:09:11.750
Right? x squared to the third--
you multiply the exponents, and

00:09:11.750 --> 00:09:16.350
then you add these. x to the
seventh over 3, minus this

00:09:16.350 --> 00:09:17.790
